&lt;p&gt;I created another ticket &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-17116&quot; title=&quot;components - Loading resource from classpath should use ClassResolver API&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CAMEL-17116&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CAMEL-17116&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Can you try to see if this code also works for quarkus:dev mode&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
